Package: photoextractor
Title: Extract Pictograms from Videos with Metadata Preservation
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Diego J.", "Lizcano", , "dj.lizcano@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9648-0576"))
Date: 2026-04-15
Maintainer: Diego J. Lizcano <dj.lizcano@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools to extract frames (pictograms) from videos while 
    preserving and stamping original video metadata (recording date and time) 
    into the extracted images. Supports batch processing of folders and 
    customizable time zone offsets.
